TEKA

   Colloquialism from the phrase “Hintay ka” (You wait)
   Téka
   Wait

   Téka lang.
   Just wait.

   Téka muna.
   Wait first.

   Téka lang po.
   Just wait please.
   (spoken to an older person)

   Other Tagalog words for ‘to wait’ are hintay and antay.

KAHULUGAN SA TAGALOG

   Ito ay padamdam na pinaikling “Hintay ka! ”
